column5: Browsing the latest online sale flyer, Canadian Tire has the Rapala Pro Select Nitro Power ice auger (8") for $280. It's marked down $170. Sale is three days only, started today and ending Sunday 25th. If this is a good auger, that seems to be a helluva decent price.
I'll stick with my Swede Bore.  I can almost keep up with a Jiffy in less than 20"
